근거: 도움말예제 | 원문: 1줄 | 의미론: 9줄 | 렌더링: 1줄 | 크기 +1단계
{{{+1 +1단계}}}
Document@0..18
  Paragraph@0..17
    SizedText@0..17
      DelimiterOpen@0..3 "{{{"
      SizeLevel@3..5 "+1"
      Separator@5..6 " "
      Text@6..14 "+1단계"
      DelimiterClose@14..17 "}}}"
  Newline@17..18 "\n"
<div class="wiki-paragraph"><span class="wiki-size-up-1">+1단계</span></div>
